dBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:32:32.000Z","msg":"蘋果直播：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/videos/704201206795360/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fvideos%2F704201206795360%2F&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=85a2db1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/videos/704201206795360/</a>"},{"pid":"89f76142217c7e48cf67a18faec9bb5ae4a9d9ab","tid":2118310,"uid":84303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcda32ffdc3aef94f00cb0268c015c8bb4d730ec","tid":2118310,"uid":17726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"睇live 發現，原來元朗可以咁多警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16343937a12f7c94213958d8abcf86d57398aac4","tid":2118310,"uid":301666,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"orange\">【7.21 一周年】堅持到元朗撐年輕人 麥婆婆：都 90 歲人，有咩好驚</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/109452565_3284232794995651_5571761815834314861_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=QaKXBAWE9RwAX-A0QmM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=432cd5748b698d7b33910b58a0155cc2&amp;oe=5F3B1B65\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F109452565_3284232794995651_5571761815834314861_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DQaKXBAWE9RwAX-A0QmM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3D432cd5748b698d7b33910b58a0155cc2%26oe%3D5F3B1B65&h=3a331178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗西鐵站附近空地，沿路大批警員戒備，一位婆婆離遠招手向記者詢問：「啲警察喺邊啊？個示威現場喺邊？你帶我去好唔好。」話落，她從掛滿黃、白絲帶的背囊中，找出一份 6 年前參與雨傘運動後被報道的新聞剪報，報道中有她的照片及名稱，她叫麥婆婆。「你信我啦，我 6 年前就參加（社運）啦，上年開始日日都出，啲催淚彈喺我腳面前我都唔驚，我都 90 歲人啦，有咩好驚。」麥婆婆沿路跟貼著，生怕走失後要重新問路。<br />\n<br />\n看見她的口罩覆蓋不了鼻子，記者提醒她要好好保護自己，戴好口罩，麥婆婆趕緊地就把口罩移上，「好辛苦㗎，戴住唞唔到氣，不過怕唔戴會被警察拉，上個月我去示威一日都無戴過&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n通往西鐵站的路有點遠，麥婆婆喃喃地說：「今日先發現元朗真係大，以前剩係識去大馬路。」「呢排好奇怪，電台都唔報有咩（抗爭）活動，搞到我咩都唔知，今日一聽到有就即刻過嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">記者問婆婆住哪兒，「我住梨木樹㗎，要轉車先過嚟，但我邊度都去過，紅磡、大埔&hellip;&hellip;」今日嚟為咗咩？麥婆婆毫不猶豫地答：「我嚟撐後生仔囉。」</span></strong>終於到了元朗站現場，婆婆看見大批警員及記者的場面，「係啊，係呢度啦！」說罷，獨自走進警察與記者之間，十分熟悉「架步」的感覺。"},{"pid":"80c992ccad9698284460f854e6d278c99681f9f0","tid":2118310,"uid":76745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12fd5ac3b38b3e7f798a37264c80ccd53fcfb0ef","tid":2118310,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1419aabd926504932f17ded8679ddabfd498933","tid":2118310,"uid":76745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"冇人有武器 班綠狗著撚晒裝做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肉酸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:32:32.000Z","msg":"試佢地件新玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"做俾外國睇 黑狗係極權打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bd594091e2d9206c2bec7934f560b44a8874b4","tid":2118310,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"今晚一齊打721國際戰線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1982796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1982796</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35a867f7bcdb781042b161e5253fe56cd6ecbfe0","tid":2118310,"uid":301666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1419aabd926504932f17ded8679ddabfd498933","tid":2118310,"uid":76745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:31:17.000Z","msg":"冇人有武器 班綠狗著撚晒裝做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肉酸到<img src=\"/ass